                     <interp inst="t18360815-1841-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> for stealing, on the 3rd if August, a coat, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360815-name-503" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-503" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-503" type="surname" value="BOSWELL"></interp>
